Description: halfBaked is a collection of convenience functions to aid in `omics analyses.
    They span functions to automate and organize repetitive analyses (e.g. many pairwise RNA-seq comparisons) to viz.
    More specifically, theyâ€™re designed to help create template Rmd notebooks to jumpstart exploratory data analysis and get the ball rolling for common data modalities.
    Several templates are provided as vignettes.
